==Useful Info==
'''Storm dragons''' are enormous, [[electricity]]-themed [[list of dragons|dragons]], faster and more deadly than their [[fire|fire dragon]]- and [[ice dragon|ice]]- themed cousins. They can often be found in [[the Depths]], [[Vaults]]:5, and [[Zot]], but nasty [[out-of-depth]] storm dragons can be found in [[the Dungeon]] (as early as D:10).

Like other dragons, killing it may drop [[storm dragon scales]] (33% chance).

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*As expected, [[electricity resistance]] helps when fighting them.
*Lightning Bolt can [[doublezap]] if it bounces off a wall, so try not to stand behind walls.

==History==
*Prior to [[0.31]], storm dragons had rC+.
